The most amazing color codes are::
-- > transparent light greyish colors for background and colors.

#ddd   ---> given by juhi
#ced0ce  ----. less heavy than above


some good color combinations are::


html body tag background: #EFECED;
centered  div block background-color: #FAFAFA;

inspiration:: 
https://neotalent.kyloe.plus/viewer/1603878088434ae20e81112ab8f4a7dfcefcc488de177673b2d8b


